* The point of no return

39:34.239 --> 39:39.043
* So we will walk
through the fire *

39:39.077 --> 39:43.581
* And let it burn

39:43.614 --> 39:48.186
* Let it burn

39:48.219 --> 39:52.458
* Let it burn

39:52.490 --> 39:55.594
* Let it burn

39:55.626 --> 39:57.996
Show time.

40:05.836 --> 40:08.106
I love a good entrance.

40:08.139 --> 40:10.275
How are you
with death scenes?

40:10.307 --> 40:12.077
(chuckles)

40:12.110 --> 40:16.246
You got a name?
I've got 100.

40:16.280 --> 40:20.318
Well, I ought to know
what to call you if you're
gonna be my brother-in-law.

40:20.351 --> 40:22.387
Buffy, I swear I didn't do it.

40:22.420 --> 40:26.090
Don't worry.
You're not going anywhere.

40:26.123 --> 40:27.992
-I am.
-What?

40:28.025 --> 40:31.797
Deal's this:
I can't kill you,

40:31.829 --> 40:34.264
you take me to Hellsville
in her place.

40:34.298 --> 40:36.266
(chuckles)
What if I kill you?

40:36.300 --> 40:39.471
Trust me, won't help.

40:39.505 --> 40:42.940
-Hmm, that's gloomy.
-That's life.

40:42.974 --> 40:47.077
Come now. Is that
really what you feel?

40:47.112 --> 40:49.648
Isn't life a miraculous thing?

40:49.681 --> 40:52.483
I think you already know.

40:52.518 --> 40:54.318
* Life's a show

40:54.351 --> 40:58.657
* And we all play our parts

40:58.690 --> 41:02.427
* And when the music starts

41:02.460 --> 41:07.132
* We open up our hearts

41:07.164 --> 41:12.302
* It's all right if some things
come out wrong *

41:12.336 --> 41:16.041
* We'll sing a happy song

41:16.074 --> 41:20.778
* And you can sing along

41:20.811 --> 41:23.313
* Where there's life
there's hope *

41:23.347 --> 41:26.552
* Every day's a gift
