48:48.326 --> 48:53.297
* When does the end appear

48:53.331 --> 48:56.067
(scoffs)
Bugger this.

48:56.101 --> 49:00.271
* When do the trumpets cheer

49:01.871 --> 49:04.342
* The curtains close
on a kiss *

49:04.375 --> 49:07.978
* God knows
we can tell the end is near *

49:08.012 --> 49:09.947
Hey.

49:11.181 --> 49:13.684
You should go back inside,

49:13.717 --> 49:17.322
finish the big group sing,
get your kumbayayas out.

49:18.389 --> 49:20.525
I don't want to.

49:20.557 --> 49:22.659
The day you suss out
what you do want,

49:22.693 --> 49:25.195
there'll probably
be a parade.

49:25.230 --> 49:27.132
76 bloody trombones.

49:27.164 --> 49:30.135
-Spike--
-Look, you don't
have to say anything.

49:30.168 --> 49:35.373
* I touch the fire
and it freezes me *

49:35.405 --> 49:38.543
-* I died
-* I look into it

49:38.576 --> 49:40.545
* So many years ago
